text.tspan: The TwinTab peripheral board is a general purpose
I/O board for Analog and Digital circuits. It has the
- Supports a range of common microprocessors
including Arduino, RaspberryPI, PIC and MSP430.
- Electric connection via standard 5 x 2.54mm pin
- Secure fastening via two Large screwholes makes
these boards useable in industrial applications.
- Fits the Hackerpads.com Docking stations and board
- Consistent wiring topology supports both Analog
and Digital Boards running at 3.3v, 5v or 12v..
Interface Pin1 Pin2 Pin3 Pin4 Pin5
Analog GND VCC Spare In Out
Logic GND VCC Spare In Out
Digital GND VCC Spare RX TX
I2C GND VCC Spare SDA SCL
SPI GND VCC CLK DI DO
- Various Sensors ie GPS, Temperature, PIR, RFID
